Token.Abstract: A collection of useful and convenient additions for NSURL to deal with keychains.
Returns the URL of the current user's keychain directory: ~/Library/Keychains.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An URL of the current user's keychain directory: ~/Library/Keychains.

Token.Abstract: Returns the URL of the system directory: /Library/Keychains.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An URL of the system keychain directory: /Library/Keychains.

Token.Abstract: Returns an NSURL object specifying the location of login.keychain for current user.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An NSURL object specifying the location of login.keychain for current user.

Token.Abstract: Returns an NSURL object specifying the location of System.keychain.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An NSURL object specifying the location of System.keychain.

Token.Abstract: Returns the URL of the temporary directory for current user.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An URL specifing the location of temporary directory for current user. If no such directory is currently available, returns nil.

Token.Abstract: Returns the URL of the current user's or application's home directory, depending on the platform.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An URL specifing the location of home directory for current user.
